    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make Winter Fuel Payments means tested",
        "additional_details": "People receiving state pension but who have adequate income should not receive Winter Fuel Payments.\r\n \r\nBy making these payments only available to people on means-tested benefits, the same amount of money could be used to give people in need a bigger payment so they can better afford to heat their homes. This could be more effective at reducing the yearly deaths due to cold weather.",
        "background": "The Government should focus Winter Fuel Payments on people who need them most, by only paying these to people who are in receipt of a means-tested benefit.",
